    <div class="documentTop">
      <h1>Press centre</h1>
      
      <p>The Department of Information communicate questions from the press to the political leadership and departments. The department helps the press and the public to find the right department for comment, background information and case information. Information Department is responsible for the Ministry's website.</p>
<p><strong>Information department's press phone + 47 90 23 10 93 is staffed every weekday between&nbsp;0800 and 1545. Besides this, you may contact the communications director Hanne Gjørtz, tel. 95 75 52 13.</strong></p>
